Vic. Planta de Gas La Vertiente, 18.8 km by combination of old road and new highway under construction E of center of Villa Montes on way to Paraguay. Flat chaco shrubland with a discontinuous overstory of Aspidopserma quebrachoblanco, and with Celtis chichape, Caesalpinia paraguariensis and a few other species. With Castela coccinea, Quiabentia verticillata, Pereskia sacharosa, and in understory Bromelia serra and Ruprectia triflora are common.
